      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SISTER PATRICK (7) form this prep has been excellent and she made it two from two when successful at her latest appearance over 1800m at this track, getting home by 4 metres. Tactics will be crucial from this wide draw. Meets a similar line up and she is all set to salute again. MAORI TATTOO (8) was struggling to make his mark before the latest appearance when he scored by 3.5 metres over 2230m at this track. Can settle just behind them and wait on the sprint lane. This doesn't look as hard so he is a major player again. ALDEBARAN MARCUS (3) is better than his last-start run for eighth over 2240m at Melton would suggest. Each-way claims. SPEAKS VOLUMES (6) was out of the money two starts ago then things went wrong last start when he broke and finished a distant last over 2070m at Gawler. Has the talent to make his presence felt.",
